            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Gaidoinus">Gaidoin</name></persName> filio bone
                        memorie <persName><name ref="Filimari">Filimari</name></persName>
                        <foreign>pro anima</foreign> a fundamentis <rs key="#Private_foundations"
                            >construxi</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> in onure <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Private_foundations" ref="#juridical_persons/616">Domini
                            et Salvaturis nostri Iesu Christi</orgName> in territurio meo in loco
                            <placeName key="#Churches #Private_foundations" ref="#places/1020"
                            >Nobule</placeName>; <foreign>ed ora la dota di beni</foreign>: in
                        primis <rs key="#Casalini/fundamenta">fundamento</rs> ubi ipsa ecclesia
                        supraposita est, cum <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis</rs> et
                        omnibus edificiis et fundamentis, una cum curte, <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">orto</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">terris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Oil">olivetis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pratis, pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Acorns">silvis,
                            virgareis,</rs>
                        <rs key="#Chestnuts">castanatis</rs>, cultum adque incultum, <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casas massaricias et aldionales</rs>,
                        cum omnem rem ad ipsas casas pertinentes (…) <rs key="#Slave_labour #Slave"
                            >servos, ancillas</rs>, <rs key="#Aldius">aldionibus et aldianes</rs>
                        mihi pertenentibus, omnia quidquid in quemlibet loco aliquid havire visu sum
                        pertenentes ad <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> mea in predicto loco <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Casalini/fundamenta #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Fruits/vegetables #Chestnuts #Acorn #Hay/fodder #Slave_labour #Slave #Aldius"
                            ref="#places/1020">Nobule</placeName> (…). Insimul et una <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> mea massaricia in <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie" ref="#places/1018">Quesa</placeName>,
                            <placeName key="#Vici #Casae/cassinae_massaricie" ref="#places/1019"><rs
                                key="#Vici">vico</rs> ubi dicitur Piniano</placeName>, qui regitur
                        per <persName key="#Freeborn"><name ref="Pettulus">Pettulo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">homo liver</rs>, cum omnia pertenente ad ipsa casa, una
                        cum muliere ipsius Pettuli et infantes eius. Pro remedium anime quondam
                        filii mei <persName><name ref="Filo">Filoni</name></persName>
                        <foreign>fa questa donazione, riservandosi la gestione vitalizia dei
                            beni</foreign>. Et si post decesso meo ipsa ecclesia inordinata
                        remanseret, volo ut quis de filiis et nepotibus meis tonso capite cum omnem
                        rem suam in integrum in ipsa Dei ecclesia se offerre voluerit, caste et
                        recte moderamine Deo et ad ipsa ecclesia servire ligibus voluerit,
                            <foreign>possa reggere la chiesa e i suoi beni</foreign> et susceptione
                        peregrinorum et elemosina faciendi. <foreign>Altrimenti i suoi eredi abbiano
                            facoltà di scegliere un degno prete per reggerla, ma non di esercitare
                            potere sulla chiesa. Pena per gli eredi se non lo faranno o cercheranno
                            di sottrarre i beni della chiesa</foreign>: ad <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopum</rs>, qui tunc in <rs key="#Cities">civitate </rs><placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Lucense</placeName> ordinatus fuerit, auri solidos
                        numero quadringenti, quod sunt quattuor centinaria. (…) Actum in
                        suprascripto loco <placeName ref="#places/1020">Nobule</placeName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Gaidoin; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Priests"><name ref="Deusdedit"
                            >Deusdedit</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Ansfrit">Ansfrid</name></persName>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Priests"><name ref="Filosofronius"
                            >Filosofronius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>; + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Gumbertus"
                                >Gunpert</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Firmus">Fermuns</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">vir devotus</rs> testis; + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Richibrandus">Richiprand</name></persName>
                        filio quondam <persName><name ref="Deusdedit">Deusdedi</name></persName>
                        testis; (ss) <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus"
                                >Teudipert</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Gairepertus">Gairepert</name></persName>;.
                            <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName key="#Writer"><name
                                ref="Sigebrandus">Sichiprand</name></persName>.
                            <foreign>Copia</foreign>: <persName key="#Copyist"><name
                                ref="Sigebrandus">Sichiprand</name></persName>. </ab>
                        </div>
